# TS/JS PRACTICES

- Default to TypeScript; strict mode on.
- Scripts: `dev`, `build`, `start`, `lint`, `test`.
- Keep imports absolute via `paths` mapping; no deep relative spaghetti.
- Small pure functions > massive utils; add JSDoc for public exports.
